et me wrong in any position other than an assist position i'll use my lsoee in a heartbeat just such a great ratio great weapon for general damage output but not fast enuf for ma stuff. what lvl does the chanter get aggro buffs? are these drop only? and where can i get some for my chanter? <p><HTML><BODY>
