<br>
There are two versions of the chanter agro buff -- 10% and 30%. The 30% ones are mid 50's, drop in ssra and other places that drop the upper-level spells (ssra, akheva, i'm sure more like grieg's etc -- not fungus). The lower ones are storebought and are mid 30's spells if I remember correctly. Even the 10% ones do a lot, if you're close, they will bump you to the top of the list every time. They were make or break for me in HoT before I hit 60.<br>
<br>
Daramin Anklebiter<br>
Warlord of Xev<br>
